    "collapsible_content_YNH6m9": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_tab_FKCPCx": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is Myo + D-Chiro Inositol?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Myo-Inositol and D-Chiro-Inositol are naturally occurring compounds that play crucial roles in insulin signaling and cellular metabolism. Our product combines these in a clinically-studied 40:1 ratio, mirroring your body's optimal balance, to support hormonal balance, mood and metabolic health. </p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_M6bwYq": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How much should I take?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The recommended dosage is 2 scoops (4g) daily. Or as advised by your healthcare provider. Always consult a professional before starting any new supplement regimen.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_rFXTj6": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is GLUT4?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>GLUT4 is a protein that helps transport glucose into cells. Inositol supports GLUT4 activation, which can improve insulin sensitivity and glucose metabolism.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_JCak74": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can you get inositol from diet alone?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>While inositol is found in some foods, it's challenging to get therapeutic amounts from diet alone. For example, you would need to eat 8 cantaloupe melons daily to match the inositol content in just 2 scoops of our powder. Modern farming practices have also reduced inositol content in many foods.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_cpaVif": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why powder?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Our powder ensures flexible dosing and better absorption, delivering the same dose as 6-8 capsules with just 1-2 scoops. It can be mixed into drinks or food for convenient consumption. </p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_PjbiRr": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
